{
  "id": "adv_bond_aoi_01_05",
  "title": "井川葵5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "地図によると、このまま真っ直ぐ行けば着くみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "According to the map‚ it looks like we’ll arrive if we keep going straight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.3333332999996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、『牛鳴きトンネル』って妙な名前だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But \"Cow-Mooing Tunnel\" is a strange name‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 10.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "どこからか、鳴き声が聞こえてくるみたいですよ\nなんでも、牛さんの怨霊がさまよっているんだとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you can hear crying coming from somewhere.\nThey say the vengeful spirit of a cow wanders around…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.5333324432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、ホラー映画の題材にもなった場所ですよね\nなんだかこの道も雰囲気がありますし……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of a place that was the subject of a horror movie!\nThis path has such a creepy atmosphere too…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.6666657765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "牛の怨霊、ね。そういえば今日はまだ牛乳を\n飲んでないから、いたら分けてもらいたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A cow spirit‚ huh. Come to think of it‚ I haven't had any\nmilk today‚ so if it's there‚ I'd like to get some.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6666657765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.3666657765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "牛さんの怨霊の牛乳って不思議な感じがしますけど……\n本当にあるなら、飲んでみたいかも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Milk from a cow spirit feels a bit mysterious…\nbut if it’s real‚ I might want to try some…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3666657765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.8333324432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、せっかくの地方ロケなのに\n映画の聖地巡礼に付き合ってもらっちゃってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I'm sorry for making you tag along\non my horror movie pilgrimage during our local shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.3999991099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "別に構わないよ\nせっかく一緒の仕事だからね、これくらい付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind at all.\nSince we’re working together‚ I’m happy to join you for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3999991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.4666657765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、この辺りは明かりも少ないみたいだ\n何かあったら大変だし、僕が千紗を守らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ there aren't many lights around here.\nIt'd be bad if something happened‚ so I have to protect you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4666657765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.5333324432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇぇ……！？　葵さん、かっこいい……\nじゃあ、改めてよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-whoa…!? Aoi-san‚ you're so cool…\nThen‚ I look forward to your protection.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5333324432,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8766.125965200004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.2994584084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "トンネルに着いたけど、特に何も感じないなぁ\nこれなら、千紗の観てるホラー映画の方が何倍も怖いよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve reached the tunnel‚ but I don’t feel anything special.\nAt this rate‚ the horror movies you watch are way scarier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.39999911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.0999991099
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.5333324433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "丑三つ時じゃないとダメなのかなぁ。けどホラー映画の\n聖地だと思うとテンション上がっちゃいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it has to be the witching hour. Still‚ being at a horror movie\nsacred site really gets me excited!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5333324433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.8333324433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "映画だと、主人公が向こうから歩いてきて\nトンネルの前のこの辺りで、急に鳴き声が……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the movie‚ the protagonist is walking from over there\nand right here in front of the tunnel‚ suddenly a cry…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8333324433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 102.2333304089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？　待って、今何か聞こえなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Wait‚ did you just hear something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2333304089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 108.0333304089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　私には何も……\n葵さん、何か聞こえたんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? I didn't hear anything…\nAoi-san‚ did you hear something!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0333304089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.7666637422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "何かっていうか、この鳴き声って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just \"something‚\" this cry is…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7666637422,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_dog-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4566.6666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.6333304089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "うわあっっっ！？\nい、い、犬！　千紗、犬がいるよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaahhh!?\nA d-d-dog! Chisa‚ there’s a dog!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.6333304089,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.999999899992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、そうですね。犬のお散歩をしてる人が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you’re right. Someone is walking their dog…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0333304089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.0333304089
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.7333304088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "って、葵さん？　なんで私の後ろに……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Aoi-san? Why are you behind me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7333304088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.8999970755
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "い、犬だけは勘弁してよ……！\nあのリード、急に放したりしないよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just please‚ spare me from dogs…!\nThey won't suddenly let go of that leash‚ will they!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8999970755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "もしそうなったら\nきっと吠えながら僕達の元に走ってきて、ガブッと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that happens‚\nit’ll definitely run toward us barking and bite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6999970755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.6333304089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_05-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、何かあったら、私が葵さんを守りますよ\n二人で、守り合いっこしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ if anything happens‚ I’ll protect you‚ Aoi-san.\nLet's protect each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6333304089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
